PrecisAppointment of MARGUERITE-MARIE GALIPEAU, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a Deputy Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and order that Mrs. Galipeau shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.
